Class Planed

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joml.Planed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class Planed
extends Object
implements Externalizable
    Represents a 3D plane using double-precision floating-point numbers.
    Author:
    Kai Burjack
    See Also:
